# Local secrets/vars for `wrangler dev` / `npm run preview`. Copy to `.dev.vars`
# (gitignored) and fill in. OpenNext maps these into process.env on the request
# path; the GenerateBaby Workflow reads them off `this.env`.
#
# Default (cached) mode needs NO real keys to exercise the funnel UI + the cached
# generation path. Set real keys only to test the live Stripe/Replicate paths.

# REPLICATE_API_TOKEN=r8_...
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
# STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8788
# PRICE_CENTS=1799

# Owner-authorized REAL generation (spends Replicate). Leave unset for cached mode.
# REAL_GEN=1
